spec_data.Name: python2-fedmsg-atomic-composer
spec_data.Description:
This is a Fedmsg consumer that listens for when the Fedora
updates/rawhide/branched repositories sync with the master mirror, and
then triggers Atomic OSTree composes.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 01:00:43 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Composes atomic trees when Fedora repositories are updated
